{"tid":1457204,"cid":5,"subCid":12,"title":"嗰嗰剩係識屌散水撚，即係大家好想見死傷？","createTime":"2019-08-12T11:23:14.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-12T12:33:46.000Z","uid":105042,"like":9,"dislike":5,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"d175fe30e46cf83bca6fbe15a3cdb0fa56c93dd7","tid":1457204,"uid":105042,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-12T11:23:14.000Z","msg":"首先今次狼來了的而且確令好多人柒咗，包括我<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n但係如果今晚真係清場，你又好樂意見到？今日有幾多個有gear?有gear又會夠頂？<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">夠喇，呢個時勢唔可以只屌發生咗嘅嘢，諗下點樣解決/檢討問題好過啦！</span></span><br />\n<br />\n1.再加強Fact check（係呀，再呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />）<br />\n<br />\n2.預咗一定有人走/留（而家仲有唔少人留緊）大家都識講現場決定，咁咪照報告班禽獸嘅動靜囉，現場會醒水㗎啦<br />\n<br />\n3.今晚分批再入機場，最遲聽日都要入<br />\n<br />\n4.要有一班人負責機場外所有support，有咩事可以隨時救人"},{"pid":"f526c9f66b1ede3a6809b464c2308a912dd4f199","tid":1457204,"uid":105042,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-12T11:23:38.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"d9b22f1304f1b0dad32ec4f9ad84ea84b38dfb4b","tid":1457204,"uid":105042,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-12T11:24:32.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"b795d78bcf473745924dc6b513f2e7707ead10bf","tid":1457204,"uid":105042,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-12T11:25:03.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"00d954de5600b9bb15bd74cbb6d98647847e351f","tid":1457204,"uid":105042,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-12T11:25:25.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"822fb6551a1cb26d11f8687dfdd3d9853ac6d48f","tid":1457204,"uid":105042,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-12T11:26:01.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"79bcbf0d49a1d7590058ac40282e6c8f999e571e","tid":1457204,"uid":105042,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-12T11:27:23.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"5e8c09612d36fff02e99e620b794ed20933c6b22","tid":1457204,"uid":105042,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-12T11:29:13.000Z","msg":"聽日一定要再入機場呀"},{"pid":"eafebe53a09783f58bfda3aa04836c05404b1785","tid":1457204,"uid":32331,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-12T11:59:52.000Z","msg":"你自己走可以，但唔好逐個逐個呼籲人走，<br />\n<br />\n唔好係機鐵呼籲人唔好入機場，<br />\n<br />\n你可以提醒人，叫人三思，<br />\n<br />\n但每個人都有自己嘅思考，會自行判斷"},{"pid":"cb216b904086a39f71c36009c6f5c8e2b5d74fbc","tid":1457204,"uid":262342,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-12T12:33:46.000Z","msg":"推"}]}